These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
City: marseilles, rome
2 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the right of the person playing scrabble##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| City        | marseilles   | rome   |
| Game   | scrabble | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, scooter
1. the person driving the skateboard is not to the left of the owner of the rabbit##8
2. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Pet   | rabbit | cat   |
| Transport      | scooter | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite
2 different pets are kept: frog, turtle
1. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the owner of the turtle##8
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Beverage          | sprite | coffee |
| Pet   | frog   | turtle     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
